Text: Morgan Stanley grew its stake in Vanguard High Dividend Yield ETF by 4.2% in the 2nd quarter. Morgan Stanley now owns 5,024,328 shares of the company's stock worth $439,026,000 after buying an additional 203,551 shares in the last quarter.
